Class RightCylinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shape
      • ThreeDimension
        • RightCylinder

  • public class RightCylinder
extends ThreeDimension
    Code for creating a right angle cylinder. Bases are parallel and have centroids lining up 90 degrees to faces NOTE: Right Cylinder is obsolete. Use RightGenericPrism instead
    Author:
    Matt Wipfler
    See Also:
    RightGenericPrism
